title: Spaceshippy! v1.5
description:
You are an Alien on Earth and it is your task to kill all Flappy Birds and Floppy Birds that you encounter! 

Fly high by tapping on the screen and kill the birds by bursting your thruster engines, but watch out for powerlines, drying laundry and wrecking balls (the ones without Miley on them).

Last but not least... don't fly too high!

Features:
- One touch controls.
- A lot of Birds!
- Lots of humor and fun. 
- No pipes but wrecking balls and drying laundry!
- Nice graphics.
- Challenging gameplay.
- Google Game Services
